      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly project or a vehicle with tons of potential? This car is ready for someone with a vision to bring it back to its former glory! It shows significant wear and will definitely need some mechanical and cosmetic attention, but it's a fantastic opportunity to own a vehicle at a very accessible price point. Perfect for a hobbyist or anyone looking for a low-cost entry into their next set of wheels!",
