    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in mint, showroom condition and has been meticulously maintained to the highest standards. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, and the body is entirely free of any dents, scratches, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin looks and smells like new, with the leather upholstery and trim showing absolutely no signs of wear. Mechanically, the car is perfect, providing a smooth and powerful driving experience with all systems functioning exactly as they did the day it left the factory. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle in truly pristine, collector-quality condition.",
