      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm looking to find a new home for my trusty ride. It\u2019s been such a reliable companion and is still in really solid shape for its next owner! It\u2019s super clean, runs great, and has plenty of life left in it. Whether you're commuting or heading out on a weekend road trip, this car is ready to roll. Come take it for a spin\u2014I know you\u2019re going to love how it handles! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
