    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_18_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_18",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a high-revving 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides crisp engagement, paired with a factory limited-slip differential for optimal torque distribution and corner-exit traction. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive VANOS system refresh and a reinforced rear subframe to ensure structural rigidity. Riding on a precision-tuned MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension architecture, the chassis offers the communicative feedback and lateral grip enthusiasts crave. While showing minor aesthetic patina consistent with a well-loved machine, the mechanical integrity remains sharp, making it a formidable tool for both B-road carving and spirited daily use.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
