    {
      "id": "sybil_19_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_19",
      "description": "This vehicle has been meticulously maintained and serves as a prime example of a well-cared-for daily driver. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish with only the expected minor road wear consistent with careful use. Inside, the cabin is smoke-free and features premium leather upholstery that remains supple and free of tears. All electronic systems, including the dual-zone climate control and high-definition infotainment suite, function perfectly. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly, benefiting from a documented history of synthetic oil changes and a recent brake service. The tires have ample tread remaining, and the transmission shifts seamlessly through all gears. This is a dependable, high-quality car ready for its next owner without the need for immediate investment.",
